Perfect, let’s define this like something you can drop straight into another doc.

Below is a structured character + sprite spec for:
	•	Player
	•	Robots (enemies/hazards)
	•	Power-ups
	•	Platforms
	•	Environment tiles
	•	UI elements

I’ll assume a pixel-art style with a base grid of 32×32 px for characters and tiles. You can scale this uniformly later if needed.

