1.3 Color & Readability
	•	Helmet: light gray with a blue-tinted visor.
	•	Suit: mid-tone color (e.g., teal or orange) to stand out from backgrounds.
	•	Jetpack flame: bright yellow–orange with 1–2 pixels of smoke.
	•	Clear outline (1 px darker border) for visibility on light/dark levels.

