6.2 Bars & Meters

Fuel Bar & Fall Meter
	•	Base bar height: 8–10 px.
	•	Use 3 sprites each:
	•	bar_bg (static)
	•	bar_fill (repeatable segment or scalable)
	•	bar_frame (outline overlay)

The fall meter should visually change color as risk increases:
	•	Low: green
	•	Medium: yellow
	•	High: red

You can handle this via palette swaps, separate sprites, or shader-less sprite variants.

