7. Sprite Atlas & Layout Recommendations

7.1 Atlases

To keep things manageable for Kaboom:
	•	characters_jetty.png – all Jetty animations.
	•	enemies_robots.png – Roller Bot, Hover Drone, DropBot + variants.
	•	powerups.png – all power-up sprites.
	•	tiles_space.png, tiles_gothic.png, tiles_business.png – platforms + deco.
	•	ui.png – icons and bars.

7.2 Layout Rules
	•	Grid alignment:
	•	Jetty & robots: 32×32 grid cells (even if sprite is slightly smaller).
	•	Tiles: 32×32 grid cells.
	•	Padding: at least 2 px padding between frames to avoid bleeding when scaled.
	•	Consistent pivot expectations:
	•	Characters & robots: bottom-center or center.
	•	Platforms: tile origin at top-left.
	•	UI: origin top-left.

